{"tid":1984520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"trump：可以對任何在海上騷擾海軍的伊朗船艦開火。","createTime":"2020-04-22T13:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T14:07:51.000Z","uid":75656,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"98ca05d6ca5eca307faba144be5d3eb61919a262","tid":1984520,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:31:14.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普(Donald Trump)今天(22日)表示，他已經指示美國海軍，可以對任何在海上騷擾海軍的伊朗船艦開火。<br />\n<br />\n在一個星期前，來自伊朗伊斯蘭革命衛隊海軍(IRGCN)的11艘船艦，在波斯灣國際海域，危險的逼近6艘美國海軍與海岸衛隊的艦艇，川普因而在今天發出這項訊息。<br />\n<br />\n川普在推特上寫道，「我已經訓令美國海軍，擊沈並摧毀任何和所有的伊朗戰艦，如果他們在海上騷擾我們的艦艇。」<br />\n<br />\n在川普發出這則推文的幾個小時之前，伊朗革命衛隊宣布，伊朗已經成功的發射了1枚軍事衛星進入地球軌道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2060959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2060959&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CqCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=f8488255\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2060959</a>"},{"pid":"1832e686e353ae2eb903c7f30c897c2d6bc2ba42","tid":1984520,"uid":104034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"油價要升了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03422a4771adff6b0089ef98417bed0358b6083b","tid":1984520,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"要開波了"},{"pid":"a8d5bb74fcc1bd74f6081d2d85ebfd6f9f36c71b","tid":1984520,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n射左粒野去邊 嶋吹到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb75a1d04fec7a262a97cda41035e2b02ed1270","tid":1984520,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/p